Started out being an angry Siri user who just want it to actually respond to my multi-lingual input queries, now I work on training neural nets to tackle learning problems. 

Have experiences with Transformer and VAE models, gaining experience in many more.

Officially, I am working on modeling and learning evolutional trajectories in viral protein sequences.

On the side, I tinkle with large language models, data synthesis and curation, and write my denoised thoughts on yxzwayne.com/gaiaprime.
